org.hibernatespatial
Class GeometryUserType

java.lang.Object
  org.hibernatespatial.GeometryUserType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, org.hibernate.usertype.ParameterizedType, org.hibernate.usertype.UserType
public class GeometryUserType
extends Object
implements org.hibernate.usertype.UserType, org.hibernate.usertype.ParameterizedType, Serializable

This class ensures that Hibernate can work with the JTS Geometry type.

To properly convert Geometry objects to database specific wrapper objects, acces is needed to a spatially enabled database dialect. This dialect can be specified as a parameter to the type. If no parameter is supplied, the default Dialect will be used (set in HBSpatialExtension).

Author:
Karel Maesen
